类 QueryWrapper

java.lang.Object
uestc.zhanghanwen.ATTCK.Wrappers.QueryWrapper
public class QueryWrapper extends Object
The encapsulation of different types of queries of all REST requests of CURD requests.

    • relationshipQueryFactory

      public static QueryWrapper relationshipQueryFactory(String startNodeMitreId, String endNodeMitreId, String relationship)
      Factory mode for generating QueryWrapper of querying relationship.
      参数:
      startNodeMitreId - The start node mitre id.
      endNodeMitreId - The end node mitre id.
      relationship - can be null if the above two are given.
      返回:
      Generated QueryWrapper

      Setter method for node.

      参数:
      mitreId - the id to be set.
